      <div class="casestudy-gamooga ">
        <section class="header">
          <div class="container">
            <h1 class="d-none">Gamooga</h1>
            <picture class="logo" data-aos="zoom-in">
              <source class="lazyload" data-srcset="../images/project/gamooga/gamooga-logo.webp" />
              <img class="lazyload" data-src="../images/project/gamooga/gamooga-logo.svg" alt="Gamoogalogo" />
            </picture>
            <div data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="500">
              <picture class="header-banner">
              <source class="lazyload" data-srcset="../images/project/gamooga/gamooga-banner.webp" />
              <img class="lazyload" data-src="../images/project/gamooga/gamooga-banner.png" alt="gamoogabanner" />
            </picture>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="brand container flex">
          <h2 class="page-main-head" data-aos="fade-up">Bringing power of AI to Marketing</h2>
          <div data-aos="fade-up">
            <p class="content-txt" data-aos="fade-up">
              Gamooga powers new age startups and fast growing businesses with AI
              powered marketing tools helping them to reach and engage with their
              customers. The platform delivers personalized experiences to users
              with push notification, in-app messaging, email, SMS and Web push
              notifications.
            </p>
            <h3 data-aos="fade-up">Our Role</h3>
            <p class="content-txt" data-aos="fade-up">
              Product thinking Workshop, Strategy, User flows, Information
              architecture, UI Design
            </p>
            <ul class="clearfix" data-aos="fade-up">
              <li class="float-l">
                <h3>Industry</h3>
                <span>SaaS</span>
              </li>
              <li class="float-r">
                <h3>Platform</h3>
                <span>WebApp</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="overview container flex">
          <div class="overview__content">
            <h2 class="content-head" data-aos="fade-up">Product Thinking Workshop</h2>
            <p class="content-txt" data-aos="fade-up">
              During the 2 day workshop we interacted with the founder, product head
              and core tech team to understand the business goals, their clients and
              functions of the product. It was intense interactive activity during
              which we identified, discussed and ideated on multiple pain points of
              users.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="overview__banners mr-neg-r " data-aos="fade-up">
            <picture class="overview__banners-hero">
              <source class="lazyload" data-srcset="../images/project/gamooga/gamooga-overview1.webp" />
              <img class="lazyload" data-src="../images/project/gamooga/gamooga-overview1.png" alt="gamoogaoverview" />
            </picture>
            <picture class="overview__banners-second">
              <img class="lazyload" data-src="../images/project/gamooga/gamooga-overview3.png" alt="gamoogaoverview" />
            </picture>
            <picture>
              <img class="lazyload" data-src="../images/project/gamooga/gamooga-overview2.png" alt="gamoogaoverview" />
            </picture>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class=" blog container ">
          <h2 class="content-head" data-aos="fade-up">Evolution through Intuitiveness</h2>
          <p class="content-txt" data-aos="fade-up">
            Existing systems being very complicated to use, we came up with an
            intuitive navigation structure and user flows increasing usability and
            making the product self-sufficient.
          </p>
          <div class="blog_banner" data-aos="fade-up">
            <picture>
              <source class="lazyload" data-srcset="../images/project/gamooga/gamooga-evolution.webp" />
              <img class="lazyload" data-src="../images/project/gamooga/gamooga-evolution.png" alt="gamoogablog" />
            </picture>
            <div class="blog_banner-overlap"></div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="campaignBanner" data-aos="fade-up"></section>

        <section class="motive container cf">
          <div class="motive__banners float-l" data-aos="fade-up">
            <picture data-aos="zoom-in">
              <source class="lazyload" data-srcset="../images/project/gamooga/gamooga-motive3.webp" />
              <img class="lazyload" data-src="../images/project/gamooga/gamooga-motive1.jpg" alt="gamoogamotive" />
            </picture>
            <picture data-aos="zoom-in">
              <source class="lazyload" data-srcset="../images/project/gamooga/gamooga-motive2.webp" />
