            </picture>
          </div>
          <div class="motive__content float-r">
            <h2 class="content-head" data-aos="fade-up">Simple Campaign creation</h2>
            <p class="content-txt" data-aos="fade-up">
              We broke the campaign creation to multiple steps making it easier to
              configure the settings of the campaign.
            </p>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="features">
          <div class="container flex">
            <div class="features__content" >
              <h2 class="content-head"  data-aos="fade-up">Extensive Journey builder</h2>
              <p class="content-txt"  data-aos="fade-up">
                Journey builder is the core of the product, it is used to create
                custom user journeys and configure marketing activities accordingly.
                We have introduced multiple features into journey builder to keep it
                intuitive and easier.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="features__tags">
              <span>NEW FEATURES</span>
              <ul class="features__list flex">
                <li class="features__list_item" data-aos="zoom-in">Activity blocks</li>
                <li class="features__list_item" data-aos="zoom-in">Open Canvas with zoom</li>
                <li class="features__list_item" data-aos="zoom-in">Version History</li>
                <li class="features__list_item" data-aos="zoom-in">Keyboard shortcuts</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
          <picture class="features-banner container">
            <source class="lazyload" data-srcset="../images/project/gamooga/gamooga-features.webp" />
            <img class="lazyload" data-src="../images/project/gamooga/gamooga-features.png" alt="gamoogafeatures" />
          </picture>
        </section>

        <section class="services">
          <ul class="services__list container">
            <li class="services__list_item">
