                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="services__banner mr-neg-r" data-aos="fade-up">
                <picture>
                  <source class="lazyload" data-srcset="../images/project/gamooga/gamooga-services1.webp" />
                  <img class="lazyload" data-src="../images/project/gamooga/gamooga-services1.png" alt="gamoogaservices" />
                </picture>
